1 issues identified herein to an interim joint committee or subcommittee thereof, and to
2 designate a study completion date.
3 Section 6. The Clerk of the Senate is directed to transmit a copy of this
4 Resolution to the Governor, each member of Kentucky’s Congressional delegation, and
5 the secretary of the Cabinet for Health and Family Services, the Commissioner of the
6 Kentucky Department of Agriculture, and the commissioner of the Kentucky Department
7 of Education, for review and consideration in advancing the goals of the Make America
8 Healthy Again movement to make Kentucky healthy again.
